of your mother, grandfather...

58
00:07:15.142 --> 00:07:17.394
and, of course,
your trusty butler, me.

59
00:07:17.561 --> 00:07:20.105
- Got it all, I think.
- Oh, and, um--

60
00:07:20.272 --> 00:07:22.316
Here's a little something
from your grandfather.

61
00:07:22.483 --> 00:07:24.652
A spanking-new deck
of cards.

62
