- So that's it? No more takers?
- I have nothing left.

139
00:13:51.371 --> 00:13:53.915
I'll take
a whack at it.

140
00:14:06.386 --> 00:14:08.221
Take a seat,
Parker.

141
00:14:12.726 --> 00:14:14.561
Deal me in.

142
