a royal flush.

150
00:15:15.872 --> 00:15:18.458
- Love the birthday suit.
- Lookin' good.

151
00:15:18.625 --> 00:15:20.460
Oww, baby !

152
00:15:35.725 --> 00:15:37.560
Grab her clothes.

153
00:15:44.859 --> 00:15:47.404
Oh, right. Fine.

154
00:15:47.570 --> 00:15:52.951
If that's the way you want it,
then let the games begin.

155
00:15:53.118 --> 00:15:58.706
I swear I heard your evil clone
sneaking all the way up toward
the mess hall this morning.

156
00:15:58.873 --> 00:16:03.128
