It's really disgusting.

177
00:18:53.423 --> 00:18:56.759
Oh, well, if someone's sick,
dear, then I must go in.

178
00:19:00.012 --> 00:19:03.266
- Move aside, dear.
- No, no, really. I insist.

179
00:19:03.433 --> 00:19:06.686
