She's highly contagious.

180
00:19:06.853 --> 00:19:09.147
Honest.

181
00:19:09.313 --> 00:19:11.816
Actually, we're all
quite fine in here,

182
00:19:11.983 --> 00:19:16.070
unless Hallie Parker knows
something we don't know.

183
00:19:16.237 --> 00:19:20.366
Really. I insist. Open the door
and come see for yourself, ma'am.

184
00:19:20.533 --> 00:19:22.827
Stand aside, Hallie.

185
00:19:31.961 --> 00:19:34.380
Mommy !

186
00:19:39.886 --> 00:19:42.138
No ! No !

187
00:19:42.305 --> 00:19:45.183
No !

188
00:19:51.898 --> 00:19:56.777
- I told you it was a mess in here.
- She should know. She did it !

189
00:19:56.944 --> 00:19:58.821
You !
And you !

190
00:20:00.114 --> 00:20:02.658
Pack your bags !

191
00:20:24.847 --> 00:20:27.725
Okay, girls.
The rest of you...

192
00:20:27.892 --> 00:20:30.269
back to your activities.

193
00:20:32.355 --> 00:20:36.943
You two...
the isolation cabin.

194
00:21:46.095 --> 00:21:48.681
Oh, gosh,
it's stuck.

195
00:21:55.104 --> 00:21:58.315
- Thanks.
- You're welcome.

196
00:21:59.817 --> 00:22:03.904
Ah ! Oh, man !

197
00:22:13.914 --> 00:22:18.919
- Oh, here's your--
- Cuppy.

198
