Any of your
pictures ruined?

199
00:22:24.925 --> 00:22:28.721
- Only the beautiful Leo DiCaprio.
- Who?

200
00:22:28.888 --> 00:22:31.849
You've never heard
of Leonardo DiCaprio?

201
00:22:32.016 --> 00:22:33.851
How far away
is London anyway?

202
00:22:34.018 --> 00:22:36.270
Well, from here
it's 3,000 miles,

203
00:22:36.437 --> 00:22:39.523
but sometimes
it seems much further.

204
00:22:39.690 --> 00:22:44.737
- How far away is your home?
- Oh, California is way at
the other end of the country.

205
00:22:44.904 --> 00:22:48.073
Actually, here's a picture of my house.

206
00:22:48.240 --> 00:22:51.869
- Wow ! It's beautiful.
- Yeah.

207
00:22:52.036 --> 00:22:54.872
We built it when I was little.
We've got this incredible porch...

208
00:22:55.039 --> 00:22:57.041
that looks over
the entire vineyard.

209
00:22:57.208 --> 00:22:59.752
- And then--
- Who-- Who's that?

210
00:22:59.919 --> 00:23:02.213
Oh, that's my dad. He didn't know
I was taking the picture then...

211
00:23:02.379 --> 00:23:04.215
or else he would have
turned around.

212
00:23:04.381 --> 00:23:08.052
He's kinda like my best friend.
We do everything together.

