01:09:00,620 --> 01:09:02,740
Me? I don't think so.

974
01:09:02,750 --> 01:09:05,450
I don't even have 
 my 12-year-old molars yet.

975
01:09:05,460 --> 01:09:10,250
Well, take it from someone 
 who got their molars 
 very early in life, 

976
01:09:10,260 --> 01:09:15,060
being in love is a fantastic 
 mystery that takes a man 
 and a woman...

977
01:09:15,070 --> 01:09:19,160
I don't mean to be jerky when 
 you're trying to be all mushy 
